{"tid":600091,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"是要分手了嗎？","createTime":"2018-03-21T04:28:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T01:48:56.000Z","uid":177708,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"32eadd4ec9116a306ee4882a4d1f56a1bbe0ac60","tid":600091,"uid":177708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:28:01.000Z","msg":"之前發生既事可以睇呢到：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/599939/2?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/599939/2?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\n之前提到我男朋友唔覆我msg，又唔主動揾我，成個人就好似人間蒸發左咁&hellip;到啱先食飯嗰陣，有把唔識既女人聲突然間打比我，內容大致上係講唔好再煩住我男朋友，佢已經對我淡晒，又話我男朋友同佢講我滿足唔到佢，叫我自己收皮，之後就收左線&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n我當時聽完個電話都未意識到發生緊咩事，明明之前同男朋友一齊嗰時都好地地，點解佢一返intern就成個人都變晒&hellip;而家仲要多咗個唔知邊到嚟既女仔叫我唔好再煩住佢，個天究竟想我點？係咪想玩死先？<br />\n<br />\n我究竟應該點做？爭返個男朋友返嚟好定係講分手？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  話晒都一齊咗年半，自己真係有啲唔捨得"},{"pid":"c51064829bb8adb621557d47f1cae6d5167f4e68","tid":600091,"uid":165024,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:29:49.000Z","msg":"分手 完。"},{"pid":"ccfa58e27cd5734ae8a8a0f688b8fbe29295573f","tid":600091,"uid":62147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:30:13.000Z","msg":"分啦 都攤哂牌"},{"pid":"03fa80eb2994e0bbb8dab4f3d983e8d37b528ebc","tid":600091,"uid":62147,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:30:37.000Z","msg":"返intern有女屌 爽"},{"pid":"622f8760dbe68fd320b24eb36e6afa8c3ac06664","tid":600091,"uid":177708,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c51064829bb8adb621557d47f1cae6d5167f4e68","tid":600091,"uid":165024,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:29:49.000Z","msg":"分手 完。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T04:30:42.000Z","msg":"真係已經冇挽回既餘地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97506b373953719038bd1755